OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA sunny
OL,6,Fevening for most but still more cloud
OL,7,Fin the west of Argyll, this cloud
OL,8,Fedging east across Argyll overnight.
OL,9,FGlasgow and the south mainly clear.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FAnother dry day with some
OL,12,Fgood spells of sunshine, though more
OL,13,Fcloud at times around Mull and Oban,
OL,14,Fand high cloud increasing elsewhere
OL,15,Flater. Very warm.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBright
OL,18,Fand very warm much of Friday, cloudier
OL,19,Flater with chance of showers in north.
OL,20,FThe weekend warm and mostly dry with
OL,21,Fthe best of the sunshine across Argyll.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
